  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40963056_21_24086-24161",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "24086-24161",
      "markText": "一天他去拜见父亲，见父亲一言不发，脸色很难看，于是回到屋里便把嫁到严家的女儿毒死，回来报告父亲。这个被毒死的女孩儿，也就成了徐阶打倒严嵩的政治牺牲品。",
      "totalCount": 464,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40963056&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=24086&rangeEnd=24161",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e322b072710bf0e3e116d?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=24086&rangeEnd=24161"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40963056_17_5116-5189",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "5116-5189",
      "markText": "在现实面前，绝不妥协的杨继盛是伟大的，因为他历经磨难，坚持了自己的理想：舍身取义，报效国家。但妥协的戚继光，同样是伟大的，因为一个同样崇高的理想。",
      "totalCount": 384,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40963056&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=5116&rangeEnd=5189",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e322b072710bf0e3e116d?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=5116&rangeEnd=5189"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40963056_20_11253-11271",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "11253-11271",
      "markText": "正义和公道或许会迟到，却绝不会旷课。",
      "totalCount": 324,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40963056&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=11253&rangeEnd=11271",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e322b072710bf0e3e116d?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=11253&rangeEnd=11271"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40963056_21_23629-23710",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "23629-23710",
      "markText": "嘉靖四十四年四月，严嵩被剥夺全部财产，赶回老家。没有人理会他，于是这位原先的朝廷首辅转行当了乞丐，靠沿街乞讨维持生计，受尽白眼，两年后于荒野中悲惨死去，年八十八。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40963056&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=23629&rangeEnd=23710",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e322b072710bf0e3e116d?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=23629&rangeEnd=23710"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40963056_5_22390-22462",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "22390-22462",
      "markText": "只有真正了解这个世界的丑陋与污浊，被现实打击，受痛苦折磨，遍体鳞伤，无路可退，却从未放弃对光明的追寻，依然微笑着，坚定前行的人，才是真正的勇者。",
      "totalCount": 256,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40963056&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=22390&rangeEnd=22462",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e322b072710bf0e3e116d?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=22390&rangeEnd=22462"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40963056_4_17672-17712",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "17672-17712",
      "markText": "磨洋工也好，喝茶打牌也罢，只要天天在办公室坐着，让皇帝看见混个脸熟，不愁没前途。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40963056&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=17672&rangeEnd=17712",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e322b072710bf0e3e116d?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=17672&rangeEnd=17712"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40963056_9_26178-26264",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "26178-26264",
      "markText": "他没有麻药，也不用铁环，更没有塞嘴的白毛巾，只是带着一副平静的表情，不停地刮着腐肉。碗片并不锋利，腐肉也不易割断，这是令人难以忍受的剧烈疼痛，然而，杨继盛没有发出一点声音。",
      "totalCount": 247,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40963056&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=26178&rangeEnd=26264",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e322b072710bf0e3e116d?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=26178&rangeEnd=26264"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40963056_18_9634-9725",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "9634-9725",
      "markText": "但李如松不知道的是，几乎与此同时，那个曾经教过他的老先生，正躺在一所破屋之中，他已经卖光了所有的字画，贫病交加，且无人理会。不久之后，他带着满腔的悲愤静悄悄地离开了人世，年七十三岁。",
      "totalCount": 225,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40963056&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=9634&rangeEnd=9725",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e322b072710bf0e3e116d?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=9634&rangeEnd=9725"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40963056_5_4630-4657",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4630-4657",
      "markText": "“此学即所谓‘致良知’之心学，传我此学者，名王守仁。”",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40963056&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4630&rangeEnd=4657",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e322b072710bf0e3e116d?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4630&rangeEnd=4657"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40963056_9_19348-19414",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "19348-19414",
      "markText": "知其不可而为之。 我深信，这正是我们这个伟大民族的魂魄。",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40963056&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=19348&rangeEnd=19414",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e322b072710bf0e3e116d?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=19348&rangeEnd=19414"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40963056_15_16627-16694",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "16627-16694",
      "markText": "概括起来，戚继光要找的是这样一群人：四肢发达，头脑简单，为人老实，遵纪守法，服从政府，敢打硬仗，敢冲锋不怕死，具备二愣子性格的肌肉男。",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40963056&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=16627&rangeEnd=16694",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e322b072710bf0e3e116d?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=16627&rangeEnd=16694"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40963056_5_1819-1913",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1819-1913",
      "markText": "正德二年（1507），徐阶随父亲外出赶路，父亲在前面走，他在后面紧跟着。在经过一座高山的时候，徐阶一不小心，又出了点意外，当然，他并没有掉进枯井，相对而言，他这次掉的地点比较特别——悬崖。",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40963056&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1819&rangeEnd=1913",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e322b072710bf0e3e116d?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1819&rangeEnd=1913"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40963056_7_12796-12889",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "12796-12889",
      "markText": "夏言起自微寒，豪迈而有俊才，纵横驳辩，人莫能屈，虽身处宦海，仍心系天下，胸怀万民，然终为严嵩所害。 言死，嵩祸及天下。",
      "totalCount": 195,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40963056&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=12796&rangeEnd=12889",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e3e322b072710bf0e3e116d?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=12796&rangeEnd=12889"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40963056_9_31555-31625",
